My last day social media. We have our homestead in BC paid off with BTC
text: This is my last day on HN and social media. My family and I have our 5 acre homestead in rural BC paid off with BTC, and we are leaving tomorrow to make the 2 day trip there. We will be off the grid and living off Bitcoin. We have a Blockstream satellite kit, and will just use our full node to withdraw BTC into our virtual bank account when needed. Our hobbies are gardening, mycology, watercolor, and hiking. Bye bye!
